==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Dereligionize
<hw>De`re*li"gion*ize</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To make
irreligious; to turn from religion.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>He would <qex>dereligionize</qex> men beyond all others.</q>
<rj><qau>De Quincey.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Dereling</ent>⟦br⟧
